how they work.

329
00:26:45,878 --> 00:26:48,412
We will handle
the negotiations.

330
00:26:48,414 --> 00:26:51,249
If you have any problems,
just talk to Jaber. Jaber.

331
00:26:51,251 --> 00:26:54,284
Your job is to watch
the passengers.

332
00:26:54,286 --> 00:26:55,721
Both of you.

333
00:27:16,408 --> 00:27:18,876
4,000 kilometers.

334
