at night.

425
00:35:51,257 --> 00:35:53,891
- Without runway lights?
- Yeah.

426
00:35:53,893 --> 00:35:55,826
That's great.

427
00:35:55,828 --> 00:35:57,828
I don't think Rabin
will go for that.

428
00:35:57,830 --> 00:36:01,065
